{title:Power In Prayer}
{key: C}



[F/G]There’s [C]power  in [C/E]prayer, [F]power  to [C]spare  [G/F]


All  that.  [Csus/G#]you’ll [Am]ever  need,  is [D9]waiting  right [G]there.


A  [C]few   words,  a  [G]child’s  faith,  


And  it’s  [C]good  [C7]bye  des [F]pair,


[F#dim]For  there’s  [C/G]power,  so  much  [Am]power,


There’s  [Dm]po   [Em]wer   [G7]in   [C]prayer.
